item.title: Cheatsheets
item.description: Printable… but watermarked! The cheatsheets on this page are specially designed to fit printer paper, so please print some! If you find some value here, I would appreciate referrals back to this page (whoislewys.com/cheatsheets) or a mention on Twitter/Insta (@whoislewys). Compressor Cheatsheet For YEARS I struggled with using compression properly, messing with knobs ‘till I got lucky. I read so many posts online and watch advanced tutorials on YouTube that confused me even more.
